---
// Background SVG — subtle EC-style scatter on a soft brand gradient.
---

<section class="relative isolate overflow-hidden">
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-50 via-white to-brand-100 dark:from-slate-950 dark:via-slate-950 dark:to-brand-950/50"
  ></div>

  <!-- Decorative grid -->
  <svg
    class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 -z-10 h-full w-full opacity-[0.07] dark:opacity-[0.12]"
    aria-hidden="true"
    viewBox="0 0 1200 600"
    preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice"
  >
    <defs>
      <pattern id="hero-grid" width="40" height="40" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
        <path d="M 40 0 L 0 0 0 40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.6" class="text-brand-700 dark:text-brand-400"/>
      </pattern>
      <radialGradient id="hero-fade" cx="60%" cy="0%" r="80%">
        <stop offset="0%" stop-color="white" stop-opacity="0"/>
        <stop offset="100%" stop-color="white"/>
      </radialGradient>
    </defs>
    <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#hero-grid)"/>
  </svg>

  <!-- Floating EC orbits -->
  <svg
    class="absolute right-[-10%] top-[10%] -z-10 h-[420px] w-[420px] opacity-30 dark:opacity-25"
    aria-hidden="true"
    viewBox="0 0 200 200"
  >
    <g class="origin-center animate-[float_8s_ease-in-out_infinite]">
      <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="80" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8" class="text-brand-500"/>
      <ellipse cx="100" cy="100" rx="80" ry="32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8" class="text-brand-500"/>
      <ellipse cx="100" cy="100" rx="32" ry="80" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8" class="text-brand-500"/>
      <ellipse cx="100" cy="100" rx="80" ry="55" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.6" stroke-dasharray="2 4" class="text-brand-600"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="20" r="3" class="fill-brand-700"/>
      <circle cx="180" cy="100" r="3" class="fill-brand-700"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="180" r="3" class="fill-brand-700"/>
      <circle cx="20" cy="100" r="3" class="fill-brand-700"/>
    </g>
  </svg>

  <div class="container-prose relative py-20 sm:py-28">
    <span class="section-eyebrow">Quantum cryptography · April 2026</span>
    <h1 class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-4xl font-extrabold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-brand-950 sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl dark:text-white">
      Open reversible Shor's circuits over the
      <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-600 to-brand-800 bg-clip-text text-transparent dark:from-brand-300 dark:to-brand-500">
        Oath curve family
      </span>
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
      A complete implementation of Shor's algorithm for elliptic-curve discrete log —
      reversible field arithmetic, Karatsuba multiplication, Binary GCD inversion,
      coherent <code class="rounded bg-brand-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-[0.95em] text-brand-800 dark:bg-brand-900/50 dark:text-brand-200">[a]G + [b]Q</code>,
      QFT, and classical recovery — measured, classically verified, and proven correct
      via SP1 Groth16.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/oathbreaker" class="btn btn-primary">
        Explore Oathbreaker
        <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="h-4 w-4"><path d="M7 5l6 5-6 5V5z"/></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="/threat" class="btn btn-outline">Why this matters</a>
      <a href="/results" class="btn btn-outline">See the numbers</a>
    </div>

    <dl class="mt-12 grid max-w-4xl grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-4">
      {[
        { v: '2,848', l: 'Qubits (Oath-32)' },
        { v: '5.76M', l: 'Toffoli (Oath-32)' },
        { v: '91', l: 'Tests passing' },
        { v: '6', l: 'CI workflows' },
      ].map(({ v, l }) => (
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-brand-200/70 bg-white/60 p-4 backdrop-blur dark:border-brand-800/40 dark:bg-slate-900/60">
          <dt class="font-mono text-2xl font-extrabold text-brand-800 dark:text-brand-300">{v}</dt>
          <dd class="mt-1 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">{l}</dd>
        </div>
      ))}
    </dl>
  </div>
</section>
